member.summary:
Safe method for getting a strongly-typed cell value.
See for the list of valid types.
e.g. bool OK = Cell.TryGetValue<double>(double result);

member.remarks:
This method could be used to copy ConditionalFormatting object
from one sheet to another. For example:
ConditionalFormatting cf = sheet.GetConditionalFormattingAt(index);
newSheet.AddConditionalFormatting(cf);
